
## Project Architecture

```
src/
├── App.tsx                    # Router configuration
├── main.tsx                   # Entry point
├── index.css                  # Global styles + Tailwind + custom components
├── types/index.ts             # TypeScript type definitions
├── store/
│   ├── chatStore.ts           # Chat state (conversations, messages, AI responses)
│   └── adminStore.ts          # Admin state (auth, knowledge sources, stats)
├── layouts/
│   ├── ChatLayout.tsx          # Layout for AI Chat section
│   └── AdminLayout.tsx         # Layout for Admin panel (with auth guard)
├── components/
│   ├── chat/
│   │   ├── ChatSidebar.tsx     # Conversation list sidebar
│   │   ├── ChatMessage.tsx     # Message bubble with markdown rendering
│   │   ├── ChatInput.tsx       # Input with auto-resize and keyboard shortcuts
│   │   └── WelcomeScreen.tsx   # Welcome screen with suggestions
│   ├── admin/
│   │   ├── AdminSidebar.tsx    # Admin navigation sidebar
│   │   ├── StatsCard.tsx       # Dashboard stat card component
│   │   └── KnowledgeTable.tsx  # Knowledge sources table with actions
│   └── ui/                     # Shared UI components (to be extended)
└── pages/
    ├── HomePage.tsx            # Landing page with features & use cases
    ├── ChatPage.tsx            # AI Chat interface
    ├── AdminLoginPage.tsx      # Admin login (demo mode)
    ├── AdminDashboardPage.tsx  # Dashboard with stats & activity
    ├── AdminKnowledgePage.tsx  # Knowledge source management with upload modal
    ├── AdminSourcesPage.tsx    # External URL data sources
    └── AdminSettingsPage.tsx   # System settings
```

## Routes

| Path | Page | Auth Required |
|------|------|---------------|
| `/` | Landing/Home Page | No |
| `/chat` | AI Chat Interface | No |
| `/admin/login` | Admin Login | No |
| `/admin` | Admin Dashboard | Yes |
| `/admin/knowledge` | Knowledge Management | Yes |
| `/admin/sources` | Data Sources | Yes |
| `/admin/settings` | Settings | Yes |
